 background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Follows up in credit check report, liaise with credit manager.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">To responsible for front office operation during the absence of\r\nFront Office Manager (HO).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">To discuss all matters that needed to follow up with the next\r\nshift Reception Manager.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Approves the working schedule for the front office attendants\r\nand submits them to front office manager (HO).<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Conducts and ensures the neat of appearance of front office\r\nattendant as well as correct attitude and behavior, discusses problems that\r\nencountered on this point with front office manager, assistant front office\r\nmanager and their shift leaders.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.5in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Assigns and Approves Duty roster for all Front desk staffs.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">PREREQUISITES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Must\r\nbe able to communicate in English writing and speaking and other languages are\r\nadvantages. Good personality and charming is important to be the Assistant\r\nManager in the way to represent himself on behalf of hotel management.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Education:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Graduates\r\nbachelor degree and/or diploma in hotel and restaurant management or other\r\nrelated field<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Experience:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Minimum\r\nof two years of experience in similar position. Should be familiar with basic\r\ncomputer skills and previous experience in using Hotel management software’s,\r\nTelephone Switch board.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2019-08-05 18:01:22', 11, '2019-08-05 18:03:19', 11, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO `employee_position` VALUES (14, 'Front Office Manager ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">POSITION TITLE:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">&nbsp;Front Office Manager / Front Desk\r\nManager<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">REPORTS TO:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">&nbsp;Assistant manager or General Manager<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">POSITION SUMMARY:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">Directly supervises\r\nall front office personnel and ensures proper completion of all front office\r\nduties. Directs and coordinates the activities of the front desk, reservations,\r\nguest services, and telephone areas. Prepare monthly reports and budget for\r\nfront office department.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">FRONT OFFICE MANAGER\r\nDUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ol style=\"margin-top:0in\" start=\"1\" type=\"1\">\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Trains, cross –trains, and retrains all front office\r\n     personnel.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Participates in the selection of front office\r\n     personnel.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Schedules the front office staff.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Supervises workload during shifts.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Evaluates the job performance if each front office employee.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Maintains working relationships and communicates with\r\n     all departments.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Maintains master key control.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Verifies that accurate room status information is\r\n     maintained and properly communicated.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Resolves guest problems quickly, efficiently, and\r\n     courteously.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Updates group information. Maintains, monitors, and\r\n     prepares group requirements. Relays information to appropriate personnel.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Reviews and completes credit limit report.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Works within the allocated budget for the front office.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Receives information from the previous shift manger and\r\n     passes on pertinent details to the oncoming manager.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Checks cashiers in and out and verifies banks and\r\n     deposits at the end of each shift.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Enforces all cash-handling, check-cashing, and credit\r\n     policies.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Conducts regularly scheduled meetings of front office\r\n     personnel.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Wears the proper uniform at all times. Requires all\r\n     front office employees to wear proper uniforms at all times.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Upholds the hotel\'s commitment to hospitality.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Prepare performance reports related to front office.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Maximize room revenue and occupancy by reviewing status\r\n     daily. Analyze rate variance, monitor credit report and maintain close\r\n     observation of daily house count. Monitor selling status of house daily.\r\n     I.e. flash report, allowance etc.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Monitor high balance guest and take appropriate action.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ensure implementation of all hotel policies and house\r\n     rules.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Operate all aspects of Front Office computer system,\r\n     including software maintenance, report generation and analysis, and simple\r\n     configuration changes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Prepare revenue and occupancy forecasting.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ensure logging and delivery of all messages, packages,\r\n     and mail in a timely and professional manner.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ensure that employees are, at all times, attentive,\r\n     friendly, helpful and courteous to all guests managers and other employees.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Monitor all V.I.P’s special guests and requests.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Maintain required pars of all front office and\r\n     stationary supplies.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Review daily front office work and activity reports\r\n     generated by Night Audit.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Review Front office log book and Guest feedback forms on\r\n     a daily basis.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Maintain an organized and comprehensive filing system\r\n     with documentation of purchases, </span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">vouching</span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">, schedules, forecasts, reports\r\n     and tracking logs.<o:p></o:p></span></font></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n     &quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Perform other duties as requested by management.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ol><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><b>PREREQUISITES</b></span></font><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">EDUCATION:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">Minimum two-year\r\ncollege degree. Must be able to read, speak, write, and understand the primary\r\nlanguage used in the workplace.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">EXPERIENCE:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">Minimum of one year of\r\nhotel front desk supervisory experience, experience handling cash, accounting\r\nprocedures, and general administrative tasks.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', '2019-08-05 18:05:38', 11, NULL, NULL, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO `employee_position` VALUES (15, 'Front office Supervisor', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Position Title:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Front office Supervisor<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Reports to:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Front Office Manager / Duty Manager<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Position summary:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\">Primarily supervises front office team members to ensure\r\nefficient and smooth operations for producing excellent feedback&nbsp;and guest\r\nsatisfaction. Responds in a professional and courteous manner to guests by\r\nproviding accurate and timely information and services.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">You will also ensure hotel charges are processed diligently to\r\nguest\'s accounts, invoices are accurate, billing instructions are verified, all\r\nnecessary supporting bills and vouchers are attached for direct settlements.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">FRONT DESK SUPERVISOR DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">1. Ensure Outstanding customer care at all times.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">2. Maintains a friendly, cheerful and courteous demeanor at all\r\ntimes.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">3. Courteously and accurately answers inquiries from potential\r\nguests and accepts hotel reservations.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">4. Responds to telephone and in-person inquiries regarding\r\nreservations, hotel information and guest concerns.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">5. Uses suggestive selling techniques to sell room nights,\r\nincrease occupancy and revenue.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">6. Supervise daily shift process ensuring all team members\r\nadhere to standard operating procedures.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">7. Train, direct the work of, resolve issues/problems and coach\r\nand counsel the front desk team members to ensure a quality operation.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">8. Resolve customer issues, complaints, problems in a quick,\r\nefficient manner to maintain a high level of customer satisfaction and quality\r\nservice.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">9. Adhere to&nbsp;company credit limit&nbsp;/ floor limit\r\npolicies.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">10. Allocate rooms to expected arrivals after checking the\r\nguest’s preferences and special requests.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">11. Build strong relationships and liaise with all other\r\ndepartment\'s especially housekeeping, reservations etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">12. Operates the equipment, including, assisting incoming\r\n&amp; outgoing calls, setting wake-up calls, enabling DND (Do Not Disturb) and\r\npaging for in-house guests.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">13. Cross Check all billing instructions are correctly\r\nupdated&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">14. Controls cash transactions at the front desk and maintains\r\ncomplete responsibility for personal bank as specified by hotel bank agreement\r\npolicy.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">15. Supervise the operations of the front desk to ensure an\r\noptimal level of service and hospitality is provided to the guests.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">16. Performs other duties as assigned, requested or deemed\r\nnecessary by management.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font color=\"#333333\" face=\"Tahoma, sans-serif\">17. Ensure Front office log book and hotel log book is always\r\nupdated and action upon.<o:p></o:p></font></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">18. Ensures safety by following guest check in and security\r\nprocedures and reporting suspicious activity to security, manager, or MOD.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">19. Participate in hotel committees and task force assignments.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">20. Assist all departments in servicing the guests during high\r\nvolume periods.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">21.\r\nTakes responsibility in the absence of the&nbsp;duty manager or front office\r\nmanager. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">22.\r\nAs a supervisor you will be a role model, sharing your expertise and\r\ncontinually inspiring the front office team.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">PREREQUISITES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">A positive at