ize: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">PREREQUISITES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Previous experience in hospitality would be preferred and\r\nCommitment to delivering a high level of customer service. Be a good team\r\nplayer and Flexibility to work a variety of early and late shifts. Able to\r\nstand for long hours and Transport guest luggage to and from guest rooms and/or\r\ndesignated bell area.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">EDUCATION:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">High school or equivalent education. Computer Basics and\r\nknowledge of Property Management software.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">EXPERIENCE:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Previous experience working within a hotel environment in the\r\nstar / luxury market is essential Skills and Knowledge. Strong Communication\r\nskills (verbal, listening, writing), Innovative, Pro-active and reliable. The\r\nsuccessful candidate is likely to have a passion for customer service.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', '2019-08-06 09:54:21', 11, NULL, NULL, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO `employee_position` VALUES (23, 'Front Desk Agent', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">POSITION TITLE:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Front Desk Agent<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">REPORTS TO:&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Front Office Manager<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">POSITION SUMMARY:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Represents the hotel to the guest throughout all stages of the\r\nguest\'s stay. Determinate\'s a guest\'s reservation status and identifies how\r\nlong the guest will stay. Helps guests complete registration cards and then\r\nassigns rooms, accommodating special requests whenever possible.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Verifies the guest\'s method of payment and follows established\r\ncredit-checking procedures. Places guest and room information in the\r\nappropriate front desk racks and communicates this information to the\r\nappropriate hotel personnel.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">GUEST SERVICE ASSOCIATE DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Register guests and assigns rooms. Accommodates special requests\r\nwhenever possible.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Assists in pre-registration and blocking of rooms for\r\nreservations.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Thoroughly understand and adheres to proper credit, check-\r\ncashing, and cash handling policies and procedures.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Understands room status and room status tracking.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Knows room locations, types of rooms available, and room rates.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Must be sales-minded. Presents options and alternatives to\r\nguests and offers assistance in making choices.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Uses suggestive selling techniques to sell rooms and to promote\r\nother services of the hotel.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Knows the location and types of available rooms as well as the\r\nactivities and services of the property.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Coordinates room status updates with the housekeeping department\r\nby notification housekeeping of all checkouts, late checkouts, early check-ins,\r\nspecial requests, and day use rooms.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Possesses a working knowledge of the reservations department.\r\nTakes same day reservations and future reservations when necessary. Knows\r\ncancellation procedures.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">11.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Maintains guest room key storage, and maintains and supervises\r\naccess to safe deposit boxes.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">12.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">File room keys ( only for manual room key hotels)</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">13.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Knows how to use front office equipment.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">14.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Process guest check-outs.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">15.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Performing cashier related functions like posting charges to\r\nguest accounts, raising paid out\'s, currency exchange,</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">16.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Follows procedures for issuing and closing safe deposit boxes\r\nused by guests.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">17.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Works closely with the housekeeping department in the keeping\r\nroom status reports up to date and coordinates requests for maintenance and\r\nrepair work.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">18.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Uses proper telephone etiquette.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">19.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Performs cashiering tasks like bill/invoice settlement, posting\r\ncharges to the guest, paid out\'s, Foreign currency exchange etc.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">20.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Uses proper mail, package, and message handling procedures and\r\nrecord details in the courier Mail Register.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2</span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Advice guest of any messages, mail, faxes, etc. received for them.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">22.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Inform guest of the room safe and mini-bar key and room key\r\nprocedures.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">2</span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Issue parking passes/validate valet parking tickets.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">24.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Communicate services and amenities of the hotel to guests.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">25.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Obtain proper identification for tax-exempt guests and attach\r\nthe form to registration card.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">26.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Direct Bell Person to escort guest and transport their luggage\r\nto the room.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">27.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Reads and initials the pass-on log and bulletin board daily. Is\r\naware of daily activities and meetings taking place in the hotel.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">28.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Attends department meetings.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">29.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Reports any unusual occurrences or requests to the manager or\r\nassistant manager.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">30.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Knows all safety and emergency procedures, is aware of accident\r\nprevention policies.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">31.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Maintains the cleanliness and neatness of the front desk area.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">32.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Understand that business demands sometimes make it necessary to\r\nmove employees from their accustomed shift to other shifts.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">33.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">\r\n</span></span><span style=\"text-indent: -0.25in; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Advice guest of any messages, mail, faxes, etc. received for\r\nthem.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">PREREQUISITES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Education:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;High school graduate or equivalent. Must speak, read.\r\nWrite, and understand the primary language used in the workplace. Must be able\r\nto speak and understand the primary language used by the guests who visits the\r\nhotel.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Experience:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Previous hotel-related experience desired.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Physical:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Requires fingering, grasping, writing, standing, sitting,\r\nwalking, repetitive motions, hearing, visual acuity, and may on occasion have\r\nto lift and carry up to 40 pound.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', '2019-08-06 10:00:04', 11, NULL, NULL, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO `employee_position` VALUES (24, 'Front Office Cashier', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">JOB DESCRIPTION:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;Front\r\nOffice Cashier<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">REPORTS TO:&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Front\r\nOffice Manager / Chief Accountant<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">POSITION SUMMARY:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Posts revenue center charges to guest accounts, Receives\r\nPayments from guest accounts at check-out. Coordinates the billing of credit\r\ncard and direct-billed guest accounts with the accounting division.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">All guest accounts are balanced by the cashier at the close\r\nof each shift.&nbsp;He / She normally entails answering guest inquiries\r\nregarding fees and services.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Front Office Cashier Duties and Responsibilities:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list .25in\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Operates front office posting\r\nsoftware.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:.25in;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\r\ntab-stops:list .25in\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Obtains th