yle=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Independently implements appropriate hotel inventory\r\ndistribution strategy; maintains accurate rates and inventory allotments in the\r\nIDS/GDS/CRO and property PMS in a timely manner to promote rate parity\r\nthroughout all booking channels.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Develops near and long term top-line room’s revenue hotel\r\nforecasts upon request from the Regional Director of Revenue Management.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Loads all preferred, consortia and promotional rates in GDS and\r\nPMS<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Spearheads troubleshooting and resolution of any GDS rate\r\nloading issues as they occur.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Analyzes independently and determines whether hotel is\r\neffectively marketing itself across electronic distribution channels.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Participate and prepare rolling forecast and annual budget for\r\neach property using PMS and forecasting tools.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Ensure that all rooms statistics reports, including the Financial\r\nstatement, and any other related reports are accurate and consistent<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Ensure that all revenue management related systems are\r\nmaintained including Opera/Fidelio, Electronic channels, GDS, and Delphi.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Attend Weekly Sales Meeting to maintain communication of\r\nstrategies and need periods.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">In general, perform any other duties might requested by Front\r\nOffice Manager or Room Division Manager.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Perform revenue management service for a select group of\r\nhotels.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Manage all aspects of rate &amp; inventory management as\r\noutlined in the services contract.&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Lead a team of Revenue assistants, providing direction on\r\nrevenue management best practices, PMS/External Yield systems best practices,\r\nthird party channel best practices.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Creates and manages the training program of new hires to the\r\nrevenue management team.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Prepare training materials, training schedules, and systems\r\ntraining for the team members.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Experience:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Candidate should have a Bachelor\'s degree in Business or other\r\nrelated field.&nbsp; Candidate should have 2-4 years of successful revenue\r\nmanagement experience at a multi-property\r\nlevel.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Experience in hotel revenue management is important to the\r\nsuccess of this role.&nbsp; Candidate must have excellent analytical skills and\r\nmust fully comprehend the travel industry distribution landscape.&nbsp; This\r\nincludes third party channels, GDS, central reservation systems, and property\r\nmanagement systems.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Strong verbal and interpersonal skills are imperative as the\r\ncandidate will interact remotely with hotels, interact frequently with\r\ncorporate brand representation, and will coach direct reports on revenue\r\nmanagement best practices.&nbsp; Candidate must be able to effectively\r\ncommunicate ideas in verbal and written presentations.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">The right person for this position will have a demonstrated\r\nability to lead initiatives and show skills in follow up, multi-tasking,\r\nleadership and accountability for team actions.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', '2019-08-06 11:16:44', 11, NULL, NULL, 1, 3);
INSERT INTO `employee_position` VALUES (36, 'Banquet Captain ', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">POSITION TITLE:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Banquet Captain&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">REPORTS TO:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Banquet Manager / Asst. Banquet Manager&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">POSITION SUMMARY:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Primarily responsible for the supervision of the banquet staff\r\nand coordinates all food and beverage services within the banquet department.\r\nTrain the banquet team and also oversees the enforcement of hotel standards on\r\nsetting up the banquet hall, up keeping, service, break away, event courses,\r\ncleaning, staff grooming and hygiene.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">He / She should maintain and develop the highest level of guest\r\nrelations. Manage all guest requests, complaints and queries and ensure that\r\nall aspects are communicated to the respective departments (Sales, Kitchen,\r\nF&amp;B manager (HOD) etc.)&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Meet and greet guests in a friendly and warm manner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Coordinates with the event host on all aspects of the banquet\r\nfunction.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Performs planning and organization functions for the banqueting\r\ndepartment like maintaining the banquet logbook, maintaining and updating&nbsp;function\r\nsheets&nbsp;etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Checks banquet rooms, service, and kitchen areas for\r\ncleanliness, proper set up, and make sure sufficient supplies and equipment are\r\navailable for the function.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Oversee all aspects of assigned banquet function activities,\r\nensuring that food counters are properly set and ready for execution at the\r\nappointed time.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Ability to respond quickly and accurately to guest requests.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Ability to obtain any government required licenses or\r\ncertification for example liquor licenses etc.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Display good customer relation skills and take initiative to greet\r\nguests in a friendly manner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Plan the event course and orchestrates its completion in a\r\ntimely, quiet and courteous manner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Observe guests to fulfill any additional requests, to perceive\r\nwhen next course should begin, or when meal is completed.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Adhering to all banquet standard process and also hotel standard\r\npolicies and procedures.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Supervises and trains staff in the set up and break down of\r\nassigned banquet rooms according to contract and managers instructions.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Supervises and trains staff in the service of food and beverages\r\naccording to standards.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Discuss any last minute changes with the banquet team.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Ensure all guest requirements are set and ready 30 minutes\r\nbefore event start time.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Coordinates function details with banquet, conference planning,\r\nand kitchen staff.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Maintain constant contact with the banquet chef, to ensure\r\nconclusion between food production and food service.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Monitor banquet personnel in the performance of their duties.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Assist in conducting pre-shift and pre-function meetings.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Actively participates in set up of banquet rooms and service of\r\nfood and beverage to guests.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Communicates frequently with fellow supervisors and banquet\r\nmanagers as to the progress of the day’s work.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Communicates frequently with function hosts in order to ensure\r\nthat their needs are being met.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span s