dif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Guide, direct, and motivate banquet staff, Provide guidance and\r\ndirection to subordinates, including setting performance standards and\r\nmonitoring performance.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Ability to take and pass all training provided and required by\r\nthe banquet department to complete daily operational duties.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;\r\nmso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;color:#333333\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Performs other duties as assigned.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">PREREQUISITES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Must be able to speak, read, write and understand the primary\r\nlanguage(s) used in the workplace. Use judgement and reasoning to cope with\r\nemergencies such as sudden illness, accident, or interrupted service.\r\nExceptional knowledge and understanding of various banquet and food service\r\ntechniques and standards.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">EDUCATION:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolo