ify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Supervise all Room\r\nService personnel.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Respond to guest\r\ncomplaints in a timely manner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Work with other F&amp;B\r\nmanagers and keep them informed of F&amp;B issues as they arise.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Organize all documentation\r\nfor shift work on a daily basis including pre-shift reports, daily training\r\ntopics, shift floor plan, requisitions for beverage, food and sundries and\r\nmanage labor on a daily basis through the time management system.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure all staff are\r\nmeeting all established standards of service through ongoing and recurrent\r\ntraining systems<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Monitor and test service\r\nskills of staff, retrain and reinforce all standards on food and quality and\r\nservice details daily. Provide feedback and appraisals as necessary.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Coordinate and monitor\r\nall phases of Loss Prevention in the Room Service operation.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure compliance\r\nwith&nbsp;in room dining.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure the training of\r\ndepartment heads and employees on SOP’s, report preparation and technical job\r\ntasks<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">11.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Monitor and supervise the\r\nmini-bar department.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">12.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure effective\r\ncommunications between each shifts.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">13.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Supervise the room\r\nservice area in order to attract, retain, and motivate the employees.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">14.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure optimal level of\r\nservice, quality, and hospitality are provided to guest.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">15.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Regularly review house\r\ncounts, forecast and VIP list and maintain the confidentiality of the hotel and\r\nits guests<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">16.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure the timeliness and\r\naccuracy of the amenity set-up and delivery.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">17.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure compliance with\r\nall local liquor laws, and health and sanitation regulations.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">18.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure that Hospitality\r\nSuites are being set-up, serviced and broken down in a timely manner and\r\naccording to instructions<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">19.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure all staff are\r\nmeeting all established standards of service.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">20.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Monitor and maintain\r\ncleanliness of In-Room Dining areas and work areas<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">21.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Plan and conduct meetings\r\nfor outlets on a monthly basis to ensure staff is correctly communicated with\r\nand that staff are consistently trained and well-motivated. Attend\r\ninterdepartmental meetings to ensure good cross communication between departments.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">22.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Assist in the development\r\nof marketing initiatives, menu items, and other items to stimulate growth in\r\nsales for each outlet and a variety of latest market developments.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">23.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Be aware of and assist to\r\ncontrol current budgeted and forecast revenues, payroll, and product costs.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">24.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ensure all current\r\nAccounting and Human Resources policies are being adhered to. Report any issues\r\nor grievances to the Director of Restaurants and or Human Resources.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">25.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Assist in maintaining all\r\nMicros programming for food and beverage outlets.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">26.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Perform any other\r\nreasonable duties as required and directed.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">27.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Must be able to\r\neffectively communicate both verbally and written, with all level of employees\r\nand guests in an attentive, friendly, courteous and service oriented manner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">28.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Must be effective at\r\nlistening to, understanding, and clarifying concerns raised by employees and\r\nguests.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">29.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Must be able to multitask\r\nand priorities departmental functions to meet deadlines.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">30.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Approach all encounters\r\nwith guests and employees in an attentive, friendly, courteous and\r\nservice-oriented manner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">31.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Maintain regular\r\nattendance in compliance with the hotel Standards, as required by scheduling,\r\nwhich will vary according to the needs of the hotel.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">32.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Employees must at all\r\ntimes be attentive, friendly, helpful and courteous to all guests, managers and\r\nfellow employees.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">33.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Prepare and submit\r\nrequired reports in a timely manner.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">PREREQUISITES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Education:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Bachelor’s Degree in Hotel Management / Restaurant Management\r\npreferred or equivalent experience. At least 3 years of progressive experience\r\nin a hotel or a related field; or a 4-year college degree and at least 1 years\r\nof related experience.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Experience:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Two to Three years’ experience as Room service supervisor or\r\nequivalent combination of education and experience. Knowledge of food service\r\noperations and a variety of styles of services. Perform other duties as\r\nrequested by management. Maintain a warm and friendly manor at all times.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\r\n&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>', '2019-08-08 17:40:50', 11, NULL, NULL, 1, 5);
INSERT INTO `employee_position` VALUES (47, 'Banquet Event Coordinator', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:1\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-font-kerning:18.0pt\">Job Description for Banquet Event\r\nCoordinator<o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Position Title:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;Event Coordinator / Banquet Coordinator<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Reports To:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">&nbsp;Banquet Manager / Sales Director<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Position Summary:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">As an Event Coordinator you are\r\nresponsible to meet with group coordinator / event hosts prior to functions,\r\nmake introductions, and ensure that all arrangements are agreeable. Read and\r\nanalyses banquet event order in order to gather guest information, determine\r\nproper set up, specific guest needs, buffets, action stations, etc.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Working closely with the banqueting\r\nteam, he / she is responsible for the execution and delivery of all events,\r\nmaximizing revenue, utilization of meeting space and working to achieve or\r\nexceed the defined budgeted revenues for banquet department.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Event Coordinator Duties and\r\nResponsibilities:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .25in\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Preparation of&nbsp;banquet event\r\norders&nbsp;and responsible to ensure they are issued and distributed in a\r\ntimely fashion.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .25in\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Prepare all typed materials like\r\nproposals, contracts, change forms and all other inter-departmental forms\r\naccurately.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:7.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:.25in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:normal;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list .25in\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:Symbol;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Distribute Daily Events reports to\r\nensure communication to all internal departments thr