service to the guests by\r\nmeeting and also exceeding&nbsp;their expectations.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; text-align: justify; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Welcome the guests by greeting them as per the standards and\r\nrespond to customer queries by resolving issues in a timely and efficient\r\nmanner to ensure customer satisfaction.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Check the reservation\r\nbook for reservations for the next&nbsp;meal period.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Notify\r\nthe&nbsp;supervisor of any&nbsp;parties of&nbsp;more than six.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Distribute&nbsp;reservations&nbsp;among\r\nall&nbsp;servers equally, informing&nbsp;them of&nbsp;all information\r\nnecessary. Example, Birthdays, anniversaries, bill not to be taken&nbsp;to the\r\ntable or any other unusual requests.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">See that the reservation\r\nsigns&nbsp;are placed&nbsp;on the tables.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Inquire with the kitchen\r\nwhat&nbsp;the daily specials are for the shift.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Always answer the phone\r\npolitely using a friendly tone and being informative.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">The telephone must\r\nbe&nbsp;answered on a maximum&nbsp;of three rings.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">If a customer\r\nhas&nbsp;any questions, it&nbsp;is your&nbsp;responsibility&nbsp;to answer\r\nthem&nbsp;accurately. Therefore,&nbsp;know your product and price list.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">You must have complete\r\nknowledge of all food and beverage menus: The ingredients;\r\nthe&nbsp;preparation; how items are served and&nbsp;with what; know your\r\nprices; know the daily specials.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Read&nbsp;the Area\r\nInformation Magazine to know the area and what is going on.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">11.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ask the day&nbsp;and date\r\nrequired.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">12.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ask&nbsp;the time they\r\nwould like to dine.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">13.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ask how many&nbsp;in the\r\nparty.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">14.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ask if they\r\nwould&nbsp;prefer&nbsp;smoking or non-smoking.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">15.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ask\r\nunder&nbsp;what&nbsp;name they would&nbsp;like&nbsp;the reservation.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">16.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ask the phone\r\nnumber&nbsp;or room number.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">17.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Ask if there is\r\nany&nbsp;special occasion or requirements.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">18.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Once all of the\r\ninformation is obtained, repeat it to&nbsp;the customer using their name.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">19.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">All reservations are to\r\nbe printed directly into the reservation book. Never write a reservation on\r\na&nbsp;piece of paper.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">20.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Please inform the\r\nreservation that&nbsp;we will hold their reservations for 15 minutes and then\r\nwe will be releasing it.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">21.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">&nbsp;Except in emergency\r\nsituations, no employees are permitted personal phone calls or have the use\r\nof&nbsp;the telephone at any time.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">22.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">You are not permitted to\r\ngive out any personal information over the telephone. Example, Phone numbers,\r\nschedules to anyone except staff members.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">23.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">When a staff member calls\r\nto inform us that they will be absent or late, you are to inform the supervisor\r\non duty.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">24.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">All messages are to be\r\ntaken on the appropriate message pad, and not on a scrap piece of paper.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">25.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">The hostess&nbsp;is a\r\nvery important&nbsp;part of&nbsp;Your Restaurant’s experience. Always remember\r\nyou&nbsp;are the first and the last person the&nbsp;customer sees. Therefore\r\nyou are their first&nbsp;and last impression.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">26.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">It is of utmost\r\nimportance that someone is present at the hostess station at all times.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">27.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Go to the guest at the\r\nentrance and welcome them to&nbsp;Aqua and introduce yourself.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">28.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Never&nbsp;walk&nbsp;more\r\nthan three&nbsp;paces&nbsp;in front of the&nbsp;guest.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">29.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Never walk to fast.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">30.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Once at the table, pull out\r\nthe chairs for the ladies first and then any other guest you can accommodate.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">31.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Once the guests are\r\nseated, hand them the menu in their hand and tell them who their server will\r\nbe. Then tell them to enjoy&nbsp;their evening at Your Restaurant.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">32.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">On departure of a guest,\r\nyou must make contact with them. Ask them how their evening was and say\r\ngood-bye.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">33.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">If there are any\r\ncomplaints, retrieve a manager or supervisor immediately<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\