y:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Experience:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Previous\r\nexperience in similar Job role.<o:p></o:p></span></p>', '2019-08-08 17:57:23', 11, NULL, NULL, 1, 5);
INSERT INTO `employee_position` VALUES (54, 'Restaurant Manager or Assistant Restaurant Manager', '<p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">Job Title:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Restaurant Manager or Assistant Restaurant Manager<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">REPORTS TO:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">&nbsp;Food and Beverage Manager / General Manager.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">POSITION SUMMARY:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Manages\r\ndaily restaurant operations and assists with menu planning maintains sanitation\r\nstandards and assists servers and hosts on the floor during peak meal\r\nperiods.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Strives\r\nto continually improve guest and employee satisfaction and maximize the\r\nfinancial performance in areas of responsibility.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\ncolor:#333333\">DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Oversea the dining area,\r\nsupervises food and beverage service staff in accordance with operating\r\npolicies that he or she may help establish.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Creates a positive team\r\natmosphere among Team Members.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Maintains records of\r\nstaff periodic manner and operating costs.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Provides feedback and\r\ncoaching to the Team regularly.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Understands building\r\ncapability through Cross training<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Treats all Team Members\r\nfairly, with respect.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Sets high standards for\r\nappropriate team behavior on shift.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Works with food and\r\nbeverage staff to ensure proper food presentation and proper food-handling\r\nprocedures.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Handle guest\r\ncomplaints&nbsp;in restaurants.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Schedules periodic food\r\nand beverage service staff meetings to ensure correct interpretation of\r\npolicies and obtain feedback from staff members.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">11.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Maintain budget and\r\nemployee records, prepare payroll, and pay bills, or monitor bookkeeping\r\nrecords.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">12.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Check the quality of\r\ndeliveries of fresh food and baked goods.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">13.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Meet with sales\r\nrepresentatives to order supplies such as tableware, cooking utensils, and\r\ncleaning items.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0in 0in 7.5pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:Tahoma;color:#333333\">14.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\"> </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Tahoma&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333\">Arrange for maintenance