n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Oversee the operations\r\n     functions of the hotel, as per the Organizational chart.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Hold regular briefings and\r\n     meetings with all head of departments.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ensure full compliance to Hotel\r\n     operating controls, SOP’s, policies, procedures and service standards.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Lead all key property issues\r\n     including capital projects, customer service and refurbishment.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Handling complaints, and\r\n     oversee the service recovery procedures.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Responsible for the\r\n     preparation, presentation and subsequent achievement of the hotel\'s annual\r\n     Operating Budget, Marketing &amp; Sales Plan and Capital Budget.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Manage on-going profitability\r\n     of the hotel, ensuring revenue and guest satisfaction targets are met and\r\n     exceeded.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ensure all decisions are made\r\n     in the best interest of the hotels and management.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Deliver hotel budget goals and\r\n     set other short and long term strategic goals for the property.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Developing improvement actions,\r\n     carry out costs savings.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">A strong understanding of\r\n     P&amp;L statements and the ability to react with impactful strategies<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Closely monitor the&nbsp;hotels\r\n     business report&nbsp;on a daily basis and take decisions\r\n     accordingly.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Ensure that monthly financial\r\n     outlooks for Rooms, Food &amp; Beverage, Admin &amp; General, on target\r\n     and accurate.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Maximizing room yield and\r\n     hotels / resort revenue through innovative sales practices and yield\r\n     management programs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Prepare a monthly financial\r\n     reporting for the owners and stake holders.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Draw up plans and budget\r\n     (revenues, costs, etc.) for the owners.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Helping in the procurement of\r\n     operating supplies and equipment, and contracting with third-party vendors\r\n     for essential equipment and services.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Act as a final decision maker\r\n     in hiring a key staffs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Coordination with HOD\'s for the\r\n     execution of all activities and functions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Overseeing and managing all\r\n     departments and working closely with department heads on a daily basis.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Manage and develop the Hotel\r\n     Executive team to ensure career progression and development.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Be accountable for\r\n     responsibilities of department heads and take ownership of all guest\r\n     complaints.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Provide effective leadership to\r\n     hotel team members.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Lead in all aspects of business\r\n     planning.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Respond to audits to ensure\r\n     continual improvement is achieved.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Corporate client handling and\r\n     take part in new client acquisition along with the sales team whenever\r\n     required.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Assisting in residential sales\r\n     as and when required and development with strong sales prospects.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Responsible for safeguarding\r\n     the quality of operations both (internal &amp; external audits).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color:#333333;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;\r\n     line-height:normal;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\r\n     background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\n     mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\">Responsible for legalization,\r\n     Occupational Health &amp; Safety Act, fire regulations and other legal\r\n     requirements.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\r\n</ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">PREREQUISITES:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">The ideal candidate is\r\na seasoned and highly intelligent hotel professional with outstanding,\r\nmanagement skills and extensive hands-on experience. Available to work when\r\nneeded, including weekends, holidays, and nights.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">EDUCATION:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">A university degree in\r\nhotel management or a related field with Experience in opening, managing or\r\nre-positioning a hotel with clear track record. Excellent computer system\r\nskills.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">EXPERIENCE:</span></b><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-align:justify;line-height:\r\nnormal;background:white\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#333333\">At least 15 to 20 years’\r\nexperience in the hospitality industry, with significant luxury and\r\ninternational experience, ideally including experience in remote locations. And\r\n5 to 10 years of experience as a General Manager or Asst. General Manager.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n  <o:AllowPNG></o:AllowPNG>\r\n </o:OfficeDocumentSettings>\r\n</xml><![endif]-->\r\n\r\n\r\n<!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n <w:WordDocument>\r\n  <w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n  <w