INSERT INTO `item` VALUES (24, 'Siem Reap –Rolouse Group& Kampong Khleang with Tuk Tuk Only', '1DAY, Siem Reap –Rolouse Group& Kampong Khleang with Tuk Tuk Only	Departure : 08:00AM\r\n\r\nToday you will explore the earliest Angkor capital in the region Hariharalaya near the contemporary town of Rolous. In Rolous Group you will visit Preak Ko, Bakong, and Lolei temple. Then continue to Kompong Khleang, which is located on the northern edge of Tonle Sap Lake about 50km from the city center. At Kompong Khleang you will visit floating houses, floating school, and floating forest.\r\n\r\n  Note: The boat fee is $25 per person (Alone) and $20/person from 2 people up.\r\n', 'INCLUSIONS\r\n\r\n•	Tuk Tuk ( Remork) \r\n•	Mineral water\r\n', 40.00, NULL, 6, 4, 1, NULL, NULL, 19, '2019-08-29 13:59:03');
