INSERT INTO `item` VALUES (38, 'Siem Reap – Mini Tour with Tuk Tuk 2 days ', 'DAY 1 	Siem Reap – Mini Tour with Tuk Tuk 2 days 	Departure : 08:00AM\r\n\r\nToday you will visit Angkor Wat temple then you will continue to Ta Prohm temple. Next, you will visit Angkor Thom and in Angkor Thom have Bayon, Bapoun, Phimean Akas, Terrace Elephant, Leper King and Preah Palilei temple.\r\n\r\n Note: If you want to see the sunrise as well you have to add $5 extra.\r\n\r\nDAY 2	Siem Reap –Rolouse Group + Kampong Phluk 	Departure : 08:00AM\r\n\r\nToday you will explore the earliest Angkor capital in the region Hariharalaya near the contemporary town of Rolous. In Rolous Group you will visit Preak Ko, Bakong, and Lolei temple. Then continue to the road ahead and use a variety of transportation to reach Kompong Phluk. Kompong Phluk, meet some fishermen and families and you also can see floating houses, floating forest, floating school….\r\n\r\n  Note: The boat fee is $25 per person (Alone) and $20/person from 2people up\r\n', 'INCLUSIONS\r\n\r\n•	Tuk Tuk ( Remork) \r\n•	Mineral water\r\n', 38.00, NULL, 11, 2, 1, NULL, NULL, 19, '2019-08-29 14:32:44');
