INSERT INTO `item` VALUES (68, 'KHMERCOOKINGCLASSES ', 'We are very proud of our amazing chef, and you can learn to cook delicious Khmer Cuisine directly from him. Book your class, then amaze your friends when you get home with your new skills and knowledge. Cambodia has a wonderful, distinctive cuisine, but it was almost completely lost under the Khmer Rouge and the decades of war which impacted every part of life, including something as fundamental as traditional recipes and cooking skills. The Khmer Rouge burnt all books and documents they found, including cook books which were seen as bourgeois. KHMERCOOKINGCLASSESWe are very proud of our amazing chef, and you can learn to cook delicious Khmer Cuisine directly from him. Book your class, then amaze your friends when you get home with your new skills and knowledge. Cambodia has a wonderful, distinctive cuisine, but it was almost completely lost under the Khmer Rouge and the decades of war which impacted every part of life, including something as fundamental as traditional recipes and cooking skills. The Khmer Rouge burnt all books and documents they found, including cook books which were seen as bourgeois. Those dark years added to the foods Cambodians now eat. You will find foods eaten daily here that seem very unusual, such as insects, spiders, and rice paddy meat (rat) however, these foods ensured survival. Some are delicious and they have earned their place in Khmer Cuisine. Don’t worry though; our cooking classes do not include these special ingredients.  ', 'KHMERCOOKINGCLASSES', 25.00, NULL, 14, 1, 1, NULL, NULL, 19, '2019-08-29 16:11:03');
