if;\">Sideburns should not be below the middle of ear<br>Moustache and beard<o:p></o:p></span></li><br><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Moustache if worn be well trimmed and not cover the<br>upper lip.<o:p></o:p></span></li><br><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Should be clean shaven on duty. Beard permitted for<br>religious reasons only should be well trimmed.<o:p></o:p></span></li><br></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; color: rgb(122, 135, 142); text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Nails</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul type=\"disc\" style=\"margin-top: 0cm; color: rgb(122, 135, 142); text-align: justify;\"><br><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Hand and toe Nails be clean and well-trimmed. No color<br>is permitted.<o:p></o:p></span></li><br></ul><