 initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Hair should be made into a bun and covered with a net.<o:p></o:p></span></li><br><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Hair length if just up to the nape of the neck could be<br>made into a pony tail.<o:p></o:p></span></li><br><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Hair should not fall below the nape of the neck.<o:p></o:p></span></li><br><li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); margin-bottom: 7.5pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif;\">Natural color of hair to be maintained and not be<br>excessively gelled or frizzy.<o:p></o:p></span></li><br></ul><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 7.5pt; color: rgb(122, 135, 142); text-align: justify; line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Face</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><ul type=\"disc\" st